> Perceptor smiled devilish and said "Then you will love this 
> information... altought Rodimus is safe inside Maximal base, he's

"Is that so?" she sensually purred. She glanced at Perceptor then gazed up to 
the ceiling, the smirk quickly removed as quickly as it appeared. "That is 
still not enough," she growled with hate. 

Eventually, she would come up with a plan to pass along to Hydras .. the 
demise of Rodimus Prime.
